A) Handle Random data
1) Create a random number (Max number based on the dictionary)
2) take the random number, and get the item based on the random number
3) Extract the Detail of the random item
4) Output 2 random data, data A and data B
5) Assign it to 2 variables

B) Game view. (Structure of the game)
1) Always print Higher and lower inside the game
2) print compare A (Get the details frrpm handle random data)
3) print \n
4) Print VS
5) Print Against B (Get details from handle random data)

C) Game flow.

1) When the game runs. Logo are printed
2) Random data are being picked
3) Print vs
4) random data are beiong picked
5) Asked used, which have more follower
6) User choose
7) Decide which have more follower. A or B
8) get the 2nd data, make it A, and get a random data, put into B
9) Repeat this cycle until the user guessed in correctly. Track the user score. And display it
10) If corrent, print You're right. Current score and proceed
11) If wrong, Print Sorry, thats wrong. Display final score

